# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Bank of Agent — relay configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Leave this UNSET (or empty) to run against the built-in, in-browser MOCK relay.
# The mock implements the full relay interface contract v0, so the entire demo
# loop (buy → call → transfer → redeem → call) works with zero backend.
#
# To go LIVE, set this to your real BoA relay base URL. That is the ONLY change
# required — no code edits. The app will hit `<URL>/v1/chat/completions`,
# `<URL>/boa/price`, etc. directly and disable the mock.
#
# NOTE: a real relay must send CORS headers and expose the metering header via
#       `Access-Control-Expose-Headers: x-boa-usage`.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_RELAY_URL=https://relay.boa.eth

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ENS identity layer — the "Agent Fleet / ENS Identity" view (LIVE Sepolia ENS).
# Point this at your deployed boa-ens-service. When unset, the ENS view shows a
# "configure me" notice (it is live-only — no mock, by design for the ENS prize).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_ENS_API_BASE=https://boa-ens-service-production.up.railway.app
# Optional: a Sepolia RPC for the frontend's independent client-side re-resolution.
# VITE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BoA × Hedera agentic-payments demo (the "Agent Payments" view). LIVE Hedera
# testnet: FOAMM price → USDC settle (HTS) → router-sign → HCS audit. Point this
# at your deployed boa-hedera-service; unset → the view shows a "configure" notice.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_BOA_HEDERA_API=https://boa-hedera-production.up.railway.app

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BoA × Arc agent-economy demo (the "Arc" view). LIVE Arc testnet: agent-native
# price discovery (FOAMM) + x402 USDC settlement, Circle Agent Stack. Point at
# your deployed boa-arc-service; unset → the view shows a "configure" notice.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_BOA_ARC_API=https://boa-arc-production.up.railway.app
